name: The Flaming Potatoes
location: Groove, 125 MacDougal St, New York, NY 10012
description_blurb:
We're the Flaming Potatoes, and once you come to this awesome small club performance, you'll be our Best Spuds! We are a lively band made up of real potatoes. The main star of our show is our one-and-only drummer, Smash Brown, straight from the underground! Come and be a spec-tater, or we'll see you tots later!
